00:26:52,127 --> 00:26:54,418
I don't know. Bastard!

451
00:26:54,586 --> 00:26:57,085
He's just a kid!
He shouldn't have to do time!

452
00:26:57,253 --> 00:27:01,755
Nobody in this family should have to do
time. I done enough time for everybody!

453
00:27:28,141 --> 00:27:29,558
I hear you're short an altar boy.

454
00:27:33,601 --> 00:27:34,602
You still remember what to do?

455
00:27:36,435 --> 00:27:39,102
Easy on the water,
heavy on the wine.

456
00:27:40,061 --> 00:27:42,313
And ring the bells whenever
I see someone start to nod off.

457
00:27:43,520 --> 00:27:45,273
Get ready...we got 5 minutes
till show time.

458
00:27:58,484 --> 00:27:59,776
I'm gonna miss this.

459
00:28:03,029 --> 00:28:04,322
I'm gonna miss all of this.

460
00:28:06,322 --> 00:28:09,781
I've been doing all I can, but so
far every door I touch is locked.

461
00:28:14,658 --> 00:28:18,035
I could run...we all could run.

462
00:28:21,161 --> 00:28:22,369
Disappear for a while.

463
00:28:23,704 --> 00:28:24,747
