about where we go.

465
00:28:36,500 --> 00:28:39,168
You run now, you're gonna
run till you die.

466
00:28:41,753 --> 00:28:44,921
Hiding's not gonna make it go away.
People aren't gonna forget.

467
00:28:47,379 --> 00:28:48,546
