469
00:28:58,717 --> 00:29:00,134
I don't want to face it.

470
00:29:02,386 --> 00:29:04,011
I'm too scared to face it.

471
00:29:06,054 --> 00:29:07,137
I'm scared, too.

472
00:29:08,095 --> 00:29:12,097
Nobody's more scared than I am,
but you gotta do it.

473
00:29:15,556 --> 00:29:19,059
You're gonna be okay. You're
gonna make it through there.

474
00:29:20,644 --> 00:29:21,476
You understand?

